'''Lunar Night''' was a [[holiday]] celebrated on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Entralla/Legends|Entralla]]. This holiday marked the night of each year when Entralla's single [[Moon/Legends|moon]] passed closest to the planet. The [[Parade of Ghosts]] was the highlight of the Lunar Night celebration.

